modShortDescription: Default is 20% faster than vanilla. Increases swim speed to make swimming a little less arduous. Makes swimming not feel like you fell into a tar pit.
modDescription:
Turns the movement factor in water from .9 to 1.2

* Default is 20% faster than vanilla.
* Increases swim speed to make swimming a little less arduous.
* Makes swimming not feel like you fell into a tar pit.
* Can be adjusted in the xml file easily to suit your needs.
